Package de.db.derpate.persistence

Interface Dao<K,​E>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - Primary Key Class
    E - Entity Class
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdminDao, EmailPasswordLoginUserDao, GodfatherDao, IdDao, JobDao, LocationDao, TeachingTypeDao, TraineeDao
    public interface Dao<@NonNull K,​@Nullable E>
    Interface each data access object should implement, including methods to find an entry by id, list all entities, persist/update/remove an entity.
    Author:
    MichelBlank
